itunes:title: (Thurs Full Show) Why Amy's Having Trouble With Her Daughter's Halloween Costume + Did Eddie Get Hit On? + We Won More Money Than Ever Before In The Lottery
description:
With Halloween right around the corner, Amy's daughter is picking out costumes she wants to wear but Amy has an issue with them. Find out why and the other costume options Bobby texts her and what they land on. Plus, what happened to Eddie that makes him think he's getting hit on by his neighbor? Then, we have a Powerball update! We won more money than ever before...but exactly how much did we win?
